      <h3 class="c-entry-box-base__headline"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="feature" href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/6/19/18681845/facebook-moderator-interviews-video-trauma-ptsd-cognizant-tampa">Facebook moderators break their NDAs to expose desperate working conditions</a></h3>
    

  
    
      
        <p class="c-entry-box-base__dek p-dek c-entry-box-base__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek"><em>At Facebook’s worst-performing content moderation site in North America, one contractor has died, and others say they fear for their lives</em></p>
      
    

    

  
    
      
      
        
